<lb />
　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">凩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こがらし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の吹く町の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">角</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>には、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青銅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">からかね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のお前に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">跨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">またが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>つた、やはり<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">青銅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">からかね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の宮殿下が、寒むさうな<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">往来</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わうらい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">老若男女</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">らうにやくなんによ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を、揚々と見<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">下</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>して<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>でになる。さうしてその宮殿下の、軍服を召した<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御胸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おむね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>には、恐れながら白い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鴉</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">からす</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">糞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が、……<lb />
